name: Globaltech Engineering
description: manufacturer and supplier of Jigs & Fixt
overview:
Established in the year 2010, at Pune (Maharashtra, India), we, “Globaltech Engineering Solutions”, are a highly recognized as the reputed manufacturer and supplier of a comprehensive assortment of Jigs, Hydraulic Fixture, Gauges, Pressure Die Casting dies, Gravity Die Casting Dies, Plastic Injection Moulds, Casting Machining, Machine Tool Components, SPM & other Precision Machining Components.

Our Team: We are backed by a talented team of professionals, who possesses enormous experience in their respective domain assist us in achieving proficiency in manufacturing and supplying an exclusive range of products.

Our Quality Assurance: We pay attention in the manufacturing process of products in order to provide clients premium quality product range. We follow strict quality measurements in order to ensure the flawless delivery of range at client’s end. Our skilled professionals are carried out the entire production process with high accuracy, proficiency and expertise.

Client Satisfaction: We highly believe in building healthy relationship with our precious clients in order to deliver quality assured products. Our talented team of professionals makes honest effort to convince our customer’s in the best possible way.

Why Us?: Our company is a leading manufacturer and supplier of Horizontal Boring Drilling Milling Facing Machine, CNC Machine and Injection Mold, etc., that meet international norms and are highly appreciated by our clients for their stability and durability. Besides, we also offer CNC job works, VMC job work and all types of precision job works to our precious clients.
